{
  "stem": "13471.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, the answer was no, for two reasons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, everybody I ever knew in the military-- in them you know, foreign military-- was an ultra right-winger.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And anything I could not stand was having to work with some of these right-wingers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't want that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, in addition, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was very much aware of the fact that my background was not-- well, let me put it this way.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The navy belonged to the Annapolis men, and I was not an Annapolis man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was no question of me ever becoming anything like an [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Annapolis. ?] So I wanted to go back to the academic world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In September-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] no, it must have been December of '46.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shortly thereafter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "About two weeks thereafter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I went back to-- to the University of Pennsylvania, and I tried to pick up my PhD studies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had interrupted-- been interrupted seven years prior to that, remember?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I thought I could just pick up where I left-- I had to start all over again.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That seven-year hiatus--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '52, I think it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In German.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
